{"article_id":"dpU9eeP1sTQ1Fd7Y","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"President Donald Trump just sided with Russian President Vladimir Putin over the US intelligence community .","depth":4},{"id":1,"text":"That ' s because in one of their conversations during an international summit in Vietnam , Putin denied","depth":6},{"id":2,"text":"that Russia interfered in the 2016 presidential election","depth":6},{"id":3,"text":"- and Trump bought it .","depth":5},{"id":4,"text":"\" He said","depth":6},{"id":5,"text":"he did n't meddle ,","depth":6},{"id":6,"text":"he said","depth":6},{"id":7,"text":"he did n't meddle .","depth":6},{"id":8,"text":"I asked him again .","depth":7},{"id":9,"text":"You can only ask so many times , \"","depth":7},{"id":10,"text":"Trump told reporters on Air Force One Saturday .","depth":6},{"id":11,"text":"\" Every time he sees me","depth":7},{"id":12,"text":"he says","depth":8},{"id":13,"text":"I did n't do that ,","depth":8},{"id":14,"text":"and I really believe","depth":7},{"id":15,"text":"that","depth":8},{"id":16,"text":"when he tells me that ,","depth":9},{"id":17,"text":"he means it . \"","depth":9},{"id":18,"text":"It ' s remarkable enough","depth":5},{"id":19,"text":"that Trump openly admitted","depth":6},{"id":20,"text":"he just believed whatever Putin told him .","depth":6},{"id":21,"text":"It ' s even more startling","depth":5},{"id":22,"text":"when you realize","depth":6},{"id":23,"text":"that in January , the FBI , CIA , and NSA clearly assessed","depth":8},{"id":24,"text":"that Russia did interfere in the election","depth":8},{"id":25,"text":"-","depth":8},{"id":26,"text":"and that Putin was behind it .","depth":8},{"id":27,"text":"Here ' s part of that conclusion :","depth":5},{"id":28,"text":"We assess","depth":7},{"id":29,"text":"Russian President Vladimir Putin ordered an influence campaign in 2016","depth":8},{"id":30,"text":"aimed at the US presidential election .","depth":8},{"id":31,"text":"Russia ' s goals were to undermine public faith in the US democratic process ,","depth":7},{"id":32,"text":"denigrate Secretary Clinton ,","depth":8},{"id":33,"text":"and harm her electability and potential presidency .","depth":8},{"id":34,"text":"We further assess","depth":5},{"id":35,"text":"Putin and the Russian Government developed a clear preference for President-elect Trump .","depth":5},{"id":36,"text":"Trump also took the chance","depth":4},{"id":37,"text":"to go after former prominent intelligence and law enforcement officials","depth":5},{"id":38,"text":"who disagree with his Russia views .","depth":5},{"id":39,"text":"`` I mean ,","depth":7},{"id":40,"text":"give me a break ,","depth":7},{"id":41,"text":"they are political hacks , ''","depth":6},{"id":42,"text":"Trump said .","depth":5},{"id":43,"text":"`` So you look at it ,","depth":10},{"id":44,"text":"I mean ,","depth":10},{"id":45,"text":"you have [ former CIA Director John ] Brennan ,","depth":9},{"id":46,"text":"you have [ former Director of National Intelligence James ] Clapper ,","depth":9},{"id":47,"text":"and you have [ former FBI Director Jim ] Comey .","depth":10},{"id":48,"text":"Comey is proven now to be a liar","depth":11},{"id":49,"text":"and he is proven now to be a leaker .","depth":11},{"id":50,"text":"So you look at that","depth":7},{"id":51,"text":"and you have","depth":6},{"id":52,"text":"President Putin very strongly , vehemently says","depth":6},{"id":53,"text":"he had nothing","depth":7},{"id":54,"text":"to do with them . ''","depth":7},{"id":55,"text":"This isn ' t the first time","depth":4},{"id":56,"text":"Trump accepted Putin ' s account about election interference .","depth":4},{"id":57,"text":"On July 7 , the two men had a one-on-one meeting at the G20 , a gathering of the world ' s top 20 economies .","depth":5},{"id":58,"text":"There , Putin also denied Russia ' s efforts","depth":7},{"id":59,"text":"to interfere in the election ,","depth":7},{"id":60,"text":"and Trump reportedly took it at face value .","depth":6},{"id":61,"text":"Trump and Putin weren ' t scheduled to meet during the forum ,","depth":6},{"id":62,"text":"but it was always possible that they would run into each other .","depth":6},{"id":63,"text":"They shook hands at a dinner for leaders on Friday","depth":9},{"id":64,"text":"and stood next to each other during a leaders ' photo on Saturday .","depth":9},{"id":65,"text":"Trump added","depth":11},{"id":66,"text":"that he ' d now rather discuss issues like Syria and Ukraine with Putin ,","depth":11},{"id":67,"text":"noting","depth":12},{"id":68,"text":"that","depth":13},{"id":69,"text":"every time he brings up the Russia issue ,","depth":14},{"id":70,"text":"Putin is unhappy .","depth":14},{"id":71,"text":"\" I think","depth":13},{"id":72,"text":"he is very insulted by it , \"","depth":13},{"id":73,"text":"he said .","depth":12},{"id":74,"text":"After Trump ' s comments ,","depth":10},{"id":75,"text":"others might feel insulted too","depth":11},{"id":76,"text":"- especially members of the US intelligence community .","depth":11},{"id":77,"text":"Trump has , at best , a complicated relationship with America ' s spies .","depth":8},{"id":78,"text":"He frequently attacked the intelligence community ' s skills and integrity during both the campaign and the early months of his presidency .","depth":9},{"id":79,"text":"He dismisses any investigation into Russia ' s meddling as a \" hoax. \"","depth":10},{"id":80,"text":"He has repeatedly mocked American intelligence officers for the mistaken conclusion","depth":12},{"id":81,"text":"that Iraq had weapons of mass destruction , a rationale","depth":13},{"id":82,"text":"that paved the way for the 2003 invasion .","depth":13},{"id":83,"text":"Trump has likened American spies to Nazis","depth":13},{"id":84,"text":"because he believed","depth":14},{"id":85,"text":"they leaked information about him .","depth":14},{"id":86,"text":"And he spent part of his first full day in office at a memorial for the CIA ' s fallen heroes","depth":13},{"id":87,"text":"attacking the media","depth":14},{"id":88,"text":"and lying about the size of his crowd at his inauguration .","depth":14},{"id":89,"text":"However , Trump does like CIA Director Mike Pompeo","depth":8},{"id":90,"text":"-","depth":10},{"id":91,"text":"but that could be because Pompeo has no problem distorting Russia-related intelligence in Trump ' s favor ,","depth":11},{"id":92,"text":"even though the CIA told me earlier this week","depth":12},{"id":93,"text":"that Pompeo stands by the January assessment .","depth":12},{"id":94,"text":"Pompeo is reportedly in consideration","depth":10},{"id":95,"text":"to become the next secretary of state .","depth":10},{"id":96,"text":"So Trump doesn ' t seem to trust the intelligence community .","depth":10},{"id":97,"text":"That ' s his choice","depth":10},{"id":98,"text":"-","depth":9},{"id":99,"text":"but it ' s concerning that he ' ll trust Putin instead .","depth":8}],"relations":[{"parent":199,"left":135,"right":198,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":135,"left":117,"right":134,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":117,"left":103,"right":116,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":103,"left":0,"right":102,"relation":"explanation","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":102,"left":101,"right":3,"relation":"evaluation","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":101,"left":1,"right":2,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":116,"left":106,"right":115,"relation":"restatement","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":106,"left":104,"right":105,"relation":"restatement","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":104,"left":4,"right":5,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":105,"left":6,"right":7,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":115,"left":108,"right":114,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":108,"left":107,"right":10,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":107,"left":8,"right":9,"relation":"adversative","nuclearity":"NS"},{"par